Name: Enable-NetDnsTransitionConfiguration

Name: Enable-NetNatTransitionConfiguration

Name: Get-Net6to4Configuration

Name: Get-NetIPHttpsConfiguration

Synopsis: Gets the active IP-HTTPS state of a computer.
